1. Topic: Compile-Time vs. Runtime Polymorphism
Compile-time: the computer decides which method to call until the reading the code.

Runtime: the compute doesn't known which method to call until the program is running and
see the object in the memory.

best example sendnotification():
--> at complie time system known that we have to send the notification

--> at runtime user will known which type of notification system wants to send.
like push notification, email, SMS etc.

